<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><b><i>Quote:</i></b><hr> I've done some quick glancing at future weapons, and the MoSS seems to be the weapon of choice, but are there other comparable viable alternatives if I want to be different?<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END-->  <br>
